         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Year 29, Choiak 9. Nechthembes son of Horos, Heliopolite, has received through Komoapis, for the levelling of the vineyard, for 20 labourers at one obol each, 3 drachmai 2 obols.;Year 29, Choiak [9]. Nechthembes son of Horos, Heliopolite, [has received through] Komoapis(?), for the [levelling] of the [vineyard], for [20] labourers [at] one obol each, 3 drachmai 2 obols.</ab>
